---
title: ErrorBaker 技術共筆部落格
layout: layouts/home.njk
description: 從錯誤中學習，從寫作中成長
image: /img/ogimage.png
date: Last Modified
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 8
  alias: posts
  reverse: true
permalink: /{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}articles/{{ pagination.pageNumber }}/{% endif %}
---

<section class="intro">
<p>
  Hi，這是 ErrorBaker 技術共筆部落格，由一群希望藉由共筆部落格督促自己寫文章的人們組成。
</p>
<p>
  部落格的主題以 web 前後端主題居多，但其實只要是跟技術有關的主題都有可能出現。
</p>
</section>
<section class="posts">
  {% set postslist = posts %}
  {% include "home-postslist.njk" %}
</section>

{% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
<nav class="nav-pagination">
  <ol>
    {% if pagination.href.previous %}
      <li class="nav-pagination__prev">
        <a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}">‹</a>
      </li>
    {% else %}
      <li class="nav-pagination__prev nav-pagination__prev--disable">
        <span>‹</span>
      </li>
    {% endif %}
{%- for pageEntry in pagination.pages %}
    {% set isCurrent = (page.url == pagination.hrefs[ loop.index0 ]) %}
    <li {% if isCurrent %} class="current"{% endif %}><a {% if isCurrent %} aria-current="page"{% endif %} href="{{ pagination.hrefs[ loop.index0 ] }}">{{ loop.index }}</a></li>
{%- endfor %}
    {% if pagination.href.next %}
      <li class="nav-pagination__next">
        <a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}">›</a>
      </li>
    {% else %}
      <li class="nav-pagination__next nav-pagination__next--disable">
        <span>›</span>
      </li>
    {% endif %}
  </ol>
</nav>
{% endif %}